description: Raw video from a Q&A session with Jimmy Heath, who turns 90 in October, at the Tucson Jazz Institute, taking questions from high school musicians who perform as the award winning Ellington Band.  Part of a new documentary by Bret Primack, aka the Jazz Video Guy, called "Passing the Torch."  To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
title: Jimmy Heath Answers Student Questions
